{"tid":1373969,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"其實李小龍既 Be Water 係乜野意思？","createTime":"2019-07-27T16:50:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T11:16:15.000Z","uid":89160,"like":42,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"2966bada93c31c0c26d82ed52d3c9f13552c012d","tid":1373969,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:50:36.000Z","msg":"依家講 be water 似乎係指「散水」果隻 water ，每次要走、想走就會講 be water ，甚至有朋友同我講拜拜都話：「我 be water 啦，聽日見」，到底有冇人知 be water 意思係乜？<br />\n<br />\n<em>&quot;Empty your mind, be formless, shapeless, like water. Put water into a cup. Becomes the cup. Put water into a teapot. Becomes the teapot. Water can flow or creep or drip or crash. Be water my friend.&quot; ~Bruce Lee</em>"},{"pid":"fcf40c81087810cb754d6fe6bc1772dda825de1e","tid":1373969,"uid":26106,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:01:14.000Z","msg":"能聚能散"},{"pid":"6945da2965f3d2c727dbe7daceaf58fe0279b724","tid":1373969,"uid":89160,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"fcf40c81087810cb754d6fe6bc1772dda825de1e","tid":1373969,"uid":26106,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:01:14.000Z","msg":"能聚能散"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:05:44.000Z","msg":"我冇聽過人講 「be water 要人快d黎」，但近排聽過無數次「be water 快d走，留係到無意思，仲有下次」<br />\n<br />\n甚至 be water 本身係咪只係解「能散能聚」呢，我睇李小龍段野既意思似乎遠遠唔止去同留架喎。<br />\n所以我想知 be water 個意思係乜。"},{"pid":"aa489cffa5369f117e21e8f88fd1760133d9a2ad","tid":1373969,"uid":290977,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:12:30.000Z","msg":"能屈能伸咁解"},{"pid":"17a190ef08aea53697e389043baf044ee7b2fab5","tid":1373969,"uid":23416,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:13:42.000Z","msg":"be water係班和理非叫人走個時用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a5a1b1804afedf2838fb2a64715f2774a70090d","tid":1373969,"uid":167648,"like":4,"dislike":2,"s